snippet.title: GetsuFumaDen: Undying Moon Official Trailer (Steam)
snippet.description:
GetsuFumaDen: Undying Moon, will be coming soon to Steam® via Early Access beginning May 14, 2021 in Asia.

GetsuFumaDen: Undying Moon即將在2021年5月14日於亞洲以搶先體驗的形式登上Steam®

Also, check out our social media channels to get the latest news and information:
https://www.facebook.com/konami.asia.game
